pull_request.title: Improve liboqs library loading
pull_request.body:
Improved library loading for liboqs-python.
* Added environment variable for path to liboqs.so
* Included ctypes system dir search.
* Added some exception handling.

The lib search code is more generalised too, with some platform specific code being replaced.
